        <h1>&#39;Something has to change&#39;: Son of pensioner who was killed in collision with speeding cyclist says deaths &#39;inevitable&#39;</h1>
    
    
    
        <p class="publish_date">5 May 2024, 10:09 | Updated: 5 May 2024, 14:33</p>
    

    <div class="video-container">
<div class="video-facade video-facade__brightcove" id="video_facade_brightcove_6352360573112" data-video-provider="brightcove" data-video-id="6352360573112" data-account="6057949401001">
<img src="https://cf-images.eu-west-1.prod.boltdns.net/v1/static/6057949401001/6091ecce-b0df-4e81-a10a-1a157ef889b2/45840421-9cc3-48a8-b593-b60499484472/640x360/match/image.jpg" loading="lazy" />
<div class="title">
<p>LBC speaks to son of pensioner killed in fatal collision with cyclist</p>
</div>
